Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,充满汗水的四次SEX
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,腳踏车部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么今天一直跟在我后面啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是想要看你有沒有做正确
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样唷,那谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那我怎么样啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很软
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大小形狀都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你的中心往左边偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会重心太靠前面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对,你往后面点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快要比賽了,你要好好努力唷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,教练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,重心高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你,教练
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗? 对的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛,教练?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我...不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直看着你的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想着你的屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是练习的时候还是比賽时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,连睡觉时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我都想着你的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,教练,请住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,教练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你的屁股真的好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来试试触感呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
