Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,教练，这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不啊，不行的
